HEADWORD: Hemi-demi-semiquaver
<hw>Hem`i-dem`i-sem"i*quaver</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Hemi-</ets> + <ets>demi-semiquaver</ets>.]</ety>
